        <item>
            <title>为运动爱好者特别设计   Amazfit Up 开放式无线耳机发表</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/22/amazfit-up-open-ear-earbuds-launched/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=amazfit-up-open-ear-earbuds-launched</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/22/amazfit-up-open-ear-earbuds-launched/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美凤]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 05:00:05 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音乐耳机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Amazfit Up]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1270661</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>智能穿戴装置品牌 Amazfit 近日发表了新款开放式耳机 Amazfit Up，专为运动健身爱好者和追求便利的用家设计。与传统的无线耳机不同，Amazfit Up 采用夹耳式造型和开放式设计，让用户的耳道保持开放，不但佩戴起来更加舒适，亦能够保持对周围环境的感知。</p><p><span id="more-1270661"></span></p><p>Amazfit Up 耳机内置 AI 演算法，能够在通话时有效减低背景噪音，即使在嘈杂环境亦可以保持通话清晰。当与 Amazfit 智能手表配对时，用家更可获取实时运动数据更新和导航提示。Amazfit Up 每只耳机重量仅 5 克，并具备 IP54 防尘防水功能。耳机支援蓝牙 5.3 和多点连接，同时连接两部装置亦无难度。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_28294"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/28im03r9Wzg?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>售价 49.99 美元（约 389 港元）的 Amazfit Up，厂方单次充电可提供长达 6 小时续航力，加上充电盒可额外提供 18 小时的电量，而充电盒只需 2 小时即可透过 USB-C 完全充电。耳机只有黑色磨砂一个版本，机身配备实体按钮，方便用家控制播放、接听电话和启动语音助手。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.gizmochina.com/2024/10/20/amazfit-up-open-ear-earbuds-launched/">gizmochina</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/06/amazfithelioring-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Amazfit Helio Ring 开箱评测　睡觉佩戴无感</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/22/amazfit-up-open-ear-earbuds-launched/mobile-music/headphones/">为运动爱好者特别设计   Amazfit Up 开放式无线耳机发表</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
