        </item>
        <item>
            <title>网民「白撞」香港快运员工电邮　购入超平价员工机票</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/21/uo/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=uo</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/21/uo/life-tech/travel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 14:15:03 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅游]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[UO]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[平机票]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[香港快运]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1270443</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>香港快运为庆祝成立 11 周年，上周六（19 日）推出员工内部优惠机票，只需 $11 或 $110 便可购入单程机票。然而，有大量网民胡乱输入员工电邮「白撞」，尝试「撞中」员工电邮购入优惠机票。</p><p>虽然机票价钱未包含税及杂费，但加 $100 便可加购单程 20 公斤行李，飞东京羽田来回只需 $1,246 更包 20 kg 行李，价格极为优惠。持有 @hkexpess.com 电邮地址的员工只需进入相关链结就可购买，员工与机票持有人无须一同出发，且无购买上限。</p><p>由于价钱相宜并经过多个旅游网站宣扬报道后，大量网民利用假电邮或乱作员工名字尝试购入超平机票，令香港快运员工不停遭到电邮轰炸。虽然优惠机票无购买上限但名额有限，经大批网民「白撞」后优惠机票火速售罄，令一众真正合资格的香港快运员工无法购买优惠机票。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2ca7cb15461c1.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270447" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2ca7cb15461c1-533x580.jpeg" alt="" width="533" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2ca7cb15461c1-533x580.jpeg 533w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2ca7cb15461c1.jpeg 828w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 533px" /></a></p><p>此举令不少员工于 Facebook 专页 UO Secrets 中匿名发文以示不满，有员工批评旅行专页对外宣传员工优惠机票，令员工无法享有应得福利，更称不少关系疏远的亲戚朋友纷纷联络询问其员工电邮。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2101.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270452" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2101-694x489.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="489" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2101-694x489.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2101.jpg 1179w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2099.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270453" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2099-694x503.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="503" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2099-694x503.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2099.jpg 1179w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2087.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270454" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2087-694x580.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2087-694x580.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2087.jpg 1075w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>同时亦有员工批评香港快运系统儿戏，让非员工亦能轻松购买员工机票，建议公司将是次所有员工优惠机票取消。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2091.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270451" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2091-694x459.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2091-694x459.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2091.jpg 1179w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2086.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270450" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2086-651x580.jpg" alt="" width="651" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2086-651x580.jpg 651w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2086.jpg 1011w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 651px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2085.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270449" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2085-665x580.jpg" alt="" width="665" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2085-665x580.jpg 665w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2085.jpg 1032w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 665px" /></a></p><p>就网民「白撞」员工电邮购入优惠机票，不少员工建议同事将来历不明的预约取消，甚至向公司上报及报警。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2100.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270458" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2100-694x409.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="409" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2100-694x409.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2100.jpg 1179w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2098.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270459" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2098-694x476.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="476" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2098-694x476.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2098.jpg 1179w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2096.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270460" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2096-694x437.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="437" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2096-694x437.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2096.jpg 1179w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2095.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270461" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2095-694x456.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="456" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2095-694x456.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2095.jpg 1179w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2094.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270462" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2094-694x544.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="544" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2094-694x544.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2094.jpg 1148w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2092.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270463" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2092-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2092-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2092.jpg 1179w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2090.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270464" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2090-694x510.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="510" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2090-694x510.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2090.jpg 1179w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>甚至有香港快运员工借此获利，为非员工提供员工电邮或代买机票收取佣金，或构成法律责任。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2093.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270455" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2093-634x580.jpg" alt="" width="634" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2093-634x580.jpg 634w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2093.jpg 984w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 634px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2089.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270456" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2089-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2089-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2089.jpg 1179w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2088.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1270457" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2088-694x483.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="483" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2088-694x483.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/img_2088.jpg 1179w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>图片来源：Facebook UO Secrets 专页截图</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/1068291/hkexpress%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%84%AA%E6%83%A0%E6%A9%9F%E7%A5%A8%E9%81%AD%E8%A1%97%E5%AE%A2%E4%BA%82%E6%92%9Eemail%E8%B3%BC%E8%B2%B7-%E7%99%BD%E6%92%9E%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%9C%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%B3%95">Hk01</a>、<a href="https://eastweek.stheadline.com/finance/7841/HK-Express%E6%8E%A8%E8%B6%85%E5%B9%B3%E5%84%AA%E6%83%A0%E7%8F%BE%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%96%91%E7%94%A8%E5%81%87%E9%9B%BB%E9%83%B5%E6%89%AE%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E6%90%B6%E5%88%B0%E6%A9%9F%E7%A5%A8">东周网</a>、<a href="https://www.facebook.com/uosecrets/">Facebook UO Secrets 专页</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/20/uo-luggage-3-in-1/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">小红书分享香港快运行李「三合一」　网民：唔好蚀俾佢</a></li>&nbsp;<li>